{"tid":717551,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[打工仔減肥測試]","createTime":"2018-06-26T06:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T02:49:42.000Z","uid":28561,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"265c3e61c6084eb6b1abb2cedeed39a69473c920","tid":717551,"uid":28561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T06:16:05.000Z","msg":"講下背景先<br />\n23歲男 162CM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  55KG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現時返OFFICE工 10am-6pm <br />\n工作期間移動輻度接近零 除左去廁所<br />\n以前有做開GYM 但開始返工之後就懶 停左接近2年冇做運動 <br />\n體重由53kg&gt;55kg 肚腩都大左個碼<br />\n<br />\n迎排收到消息9月開始要落Site著Suit工作 唔想著衫著到咁腫<br />\n所以希望由今日開始進行為期2個月既打工仔式既減肥法<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">控制飲食+唔食Lunch+每日抽時間做3次7 mins workout</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ECxYJcnvyMw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DECxYJcnvyMw&d=vt%2BzeEWJDyQQW7dzOCDrYf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=1e650c6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ECxYJcnvyMw</a><br />\n<br />\n每日食過咩同埋有冇做運動都會做紀錄<br />\n體重體脂就會一星期紀錄一次<br />\n紀錄會由27/6開始直至27/8結束<br />\n<br />\n如果方法可行希望幫到各位想減肥既打工巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歡迎發問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc15393f301761f9374b27b767c9e1b0f0d961e5","tid":717551,"uid":28561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T06:17:43.000Z","msg":"由聽日(27/6)開始會post番對上一日既飲食+運動紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155bb4cf366c633cd35cdcd9a2c41eac17c47278","tid":717551,"uid":125079,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T17:29:14.000Z","msg":"55kg 都肥? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 男仔黎講算輕啦喎"},{"pid":"a6aa25e896e0650ff1d88d39230d45342c384c6b","tid":717551,"uid":28561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:30:27.000Z","msg":"6月26日飲食與運動紀錄<br />\n<br />\n0830 - 雪菜肉絲熟蛋米粉+凍奶茶走甜少奶<br />\n1800 -  魚肉燒賣5粒<br />\n2030 - 烚椰菜半碗+烚白菜仔半碗+烚油麥菜半碗+蒸水蛋<br />\n2230 - 7 mins workout 2次<br />\n<br />\n無食Lunch發覺好難捱到夜晚<br />\n所以收工走左去篤串燒賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外今日開始既紀錄會影埋相<br />\n等大家清楚知道我究竟每日食左乜同份量係幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf1cd371e57375d1973177d0a57cc3b8d6af83d","tid":717551,"uid":28561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"155bb4cf366c633cd35cdcd9a2c41eac17c47278","tid":717551,"uid":125079,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T17:29:14.000Z","msg":"55kg 都肥? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 男仔黎講算輕啦喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:31:38.000Z","msg":"因為我個人矮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋想練翻啲肌肉著衫都好睇少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f544aeb8c3bfdb3b5e8ec51dc7ce2fff954dfa0","tid":717551,"uid":47486,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:40:55.000Z","msg":"唔食lunch  跟住食無營養嘅燒賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705907d3bc488e38b3281c3b5d1e0535f54b2350","tid":717551,"uid":65538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:43:24.000Z","msg":"唔食lunch 係唔會幫到<br />\n你照食正常午餐，不過淨係食一半<br />\n另一半就留返晏啲再食"},{"pid":"95f7ec44a9bceb0095a317e0245660279d7e6b8a","tid":717551,"uid":28561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f544aeb8c3bfdb3b5e8ec51dc7ce2fff954dfa0","tid":717551,"uid":47486,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:40:55.000Z","msg":"唔食lunch  跟住食無營養嘅燒賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:54:34.000Z","msg":"本身冇諗住食但發覺太肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會注意番食番有營養既食物"},{"pid":"e3367a7ff28c0ead0e78a099318e58ee0b677b86","tid":717551,"uid":28561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"705907d3bc488e38b3281c3b5d1e0535f54b2350","tid":717551,"uid":65538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:43:24.000Z","msg":"唔食lunch 係唔會幫到<br />\n你照食正常午餐，不過淨係食一半<br />\n另一半就留返晏啲再食"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T02:05:57.000Z","msg":"因為我係覺得<br />\n當你每日吸收既熱量比消耗低既時候<br />\n估計身體應該就會瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以想試下<br />\n當一個人係唔食Lunch令身體減少吸收一餐熱量既同時<br />\n晚餐份量保持不變<br />\n可唔可以達到吸收既熱量比消耗低既效果<br />\n<br />\n再加上7 mins workout呢類可以持續消耗能量既運動<br />\n<br />\n睇下2個月之後效果會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c44695d25b0e2c8eb916d9780e5784fc25cd3ea2","tid":717551,"uid":4519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e3367a7ff28c0ead0e78a099318e58ee0b677b86","tid":717551,"uid":28561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"705907d3bc488e38b3281c3b5d1e0535f54b2350","tid":717551,"uid":65538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:43:24.000Z","msg":"唔食lunch 係唔會幫到<br />\n你照食正常午餐，不過淨係食一半<br />\n另一半就留返晏啲再食"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T02:05:57.000Z","msg":"因為我係覺得<br />\n當你每日吸收既熱量比消耗低既時候<br />\n估計身體應該就會瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以想試下<br />\n當一個人係唔食Lunch令身體減少吸收一餐熱量既同時<br />\n晚餐份量保持不變<br />\n可唔可以達到吸收既熱量比消耗低既效果<br />\n<br />\n再加上7 mins workout呢類可以持續消耗能量既運動<br />\n<br />\n睇下2個月之後效果會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T02:08:25.000Z","msg":"唔食晚餐好過唔食午餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100da54f8db30369e044a32ab14b603932bc8b91","tid":717551,"uid":28561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c44695d25b0e2c8eb916d9780e5784fc25cd3ea2","tid":717551,"uid":4519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e3367a7ff28c0ead0e78a099318e58ee0b677b86","tid":717551,"uid":28